                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">除非我们够柔软，才不会受伤。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="935634461">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-935634461" class="vote-count">1</span>
